quran[27{c,v,t}:
37,25,""" kya ho gaya tumhe, ab kyun aik dosray ki madad nahi karte ?"
37,26,"arrey, aaj to yeh apne aap ko ( aur aik dosray ko ) hawalay kiye day rahay hain! """
37,27,is ke baad yeh aik dosray ki taraf murrain ge aur baahum takraar shuru kar den ge
37,28,"( pairwi karne walay apne pishwaon se ) kahin ge,"" tum hamaray paas seedhay rukh se atay thay """
37,29,"woh jawab den ge,"" nahi balkay tum khud imaan laane walay nah thay"
37,30,"hamara tum par koi zor nah tha, tum khud hi sarkash log thay"
37,31,aakhir kaar hum apne rab ke iss farmaan ke mustahiq ho gay ke hum azaab ka maza chakhnay walay hain
37,32,"so hum ne tum ko b_hka ya, hum khud behke hue thay """
37,33,iss terhan woh sab uss roz azaab mein mushtarik hon ge
37,34,hum mujrimon ke sath yahi kuch kya karte hain
37,35,"yeh woh log thay ke jab un se kaha jata"" Allah ke siwa koi mabood Bar haq nahi hai"" to yeh ghamand mein aa jatay thay"
37,36,"aur kehte thay"" kya hum aik shayar Majnoon ki khatir apne mabodon ko chore den? """
37,37,halaank woh haq le kar aaya tha aur is ne Rasolo-n ki tasdeeq ki thi
37,38,( ab un se kaha jaye ga ke ) tum laziman dard naak saza ka maza chakhnay walay ho
37,39,aur tumhe jo badla bhi diya ja raha hai aُnhi aamaal ka diya ja raha hai jo tum karte rahay ho
37,40,magar Allah ke cheeda bande ( is injaam bad se ) mehfooz hon ge
37,41,un ke liye jana boojha rizaq hai
37,42,"har terhan ki lazeez cheeze ,"
37,43,aur Nemat bhari jannaten
37,44,jin mein woh izzat ke sath rakhay jayen ge takhton par aamnay samnay bathain ge
37,45,sharaab ke chashmo se saghar bhar bhar kar un ke darmain phira-ay jayen ge
37,46,"chamakti hui sharaab, jo peenay walon ke liye lazat ho gi"
37,47,nah un ke jism ko is se koi zarrar hoga aur nah un ki aqal is se kharab ho gi
37,48,"aur un ke paas nigehain bachanay wali, khobsorat aankhon wali aurtain hon gi"
37,49,aisi naazuk jaisay anday ke chilkay ke neechay chhupi hui jhilli
37,50,phir woh aik dosray ki taraf mutwajjah ho kar halaat poucheen ge
37,51,"un mein se aik kahe ga,"" duniya mein mera aik hum nasheen tha"
